China Water Project, Hydropower Rated New ‘Outperform’ at Citic

-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 
2011-06-27T01:23:41Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-27/china-water-project-hydropower-rated-new-outperform-at-citic.html
China’s water conservancy and
hydropower industries were rated “outperform” in new coverage
at Citic Securities Co.  The government plan to spend 4 trillion yuan building water
conservancy projects over the next 10 years and 54 billion yuan
on hydropower projects over the following five years, Yang Tao,
an analyst at Citic Securities, wrote in a report today.  The brokerage recommends Zhejiang Reclaim Construction
Group Co., China Gezhouba Group Co. and Anhui Water Resources
Development Co.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Gregory Turk at 
 gturk2@bloomberg.net  